      },
      "date": "2011-12-24 08:23:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nI think sanityn test_4 failure is caused by this patch: A client1 write a file , another client2 rdonly open the same file, client1 reports non-zero block and client2 report 0 block.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
