      "message": "Patch Set 7: Looks good to me, approved\n\nI am undecided about whether it makes more sense to check the simple atomic mmap case first, or if the simplicity of this is outweighed by the fact that so few files are mmapped that this would just add some useless overhead in most cases.\n\nSince this is already a rare case, there is no point in worrying about this, and we can leave the patch as it is now.",
